parameters: Neither Mother nor Sister can be saved.
A star like this shouldn't exist anymore.
We have no more reason to exist.
Well, perhaps I should try it one last time.
I shall usurp all of the star's Mana,
and devote it to Mother and Sister.
Like you, I am in despair.
I shall lend you my strength.
The power of darkness that destroys the world.
The one who used my heart was you, huh?
I thought we could walk the path to darkness together.
Can I leave the boss to you, Muracca?
Hm, a small and sweet one appeared.
The other hunters seem to be doing fine, too.
Shall I teach you effective torturing methods?
...Well, I won't let it be that smooth-sailing,
If so, it's safe for now.
There will be no more darkness.
I wanted to finish it off if possible, but...
In hunting, deep pursuit is prohibited.
